ooC: bah, I was watching for Talos' reply, but I still missed it... 
=\

-- Scryed --

Scryed nods, "Yes sir." She bows, and rises turning towards the 
room's exit in one fluid motion. As she walks out, she decides to 
take a detour and get a feel for the base. Heading down the hall 
opposite to the direction of her quarters, she admires the newer 
Maximal ship design as she makes her way to the engine room.

<I wouldn't mind taking a look at what kind of stuff they put here, 
probably the Maxi's have improved the older models I remember> She 
enters the room, and nods, as her thoughts are confirmed. She begins 
to take a closer look at the damaged machinery, noticing the 
similarities and differences from the past.

Shrugging, she continues on.


> {Talos}
> 
>     Talos leaned back in the cheer looking over the bot then 
nodded, "So far
> we seem to be gaining the upper hand over Megatron, several 
predicons
> apparently have been captured and I believe one has switched 
sides, this
> provides us an enormous tactical advantage. I welcome you to the 
crew, find
> yourselves some quarters and get some rest or visit the mess hall 
and raid
> our supplies you must be hungry or tired. When you feel up for it 
report for
> duty assignments. Dismissed."
